review:
It's so pleasure to meet Dr Balraj Naidu Garu. 

He is not just a doctor but a thorough guide for happy body maintenance. 

I had a long travel last days and after I woke up this morning, my complete left side shoulder and neck got completely frozen.

I was having unbearable pain and postpone all my scheduled works. 

When I spoke with my close friend he referred Dr Balraj Naidu. He first understood my pain areas and then diagnosed the exact reason. He put me on through physiotherapy and prescribed medication.  

I am very happy,  the pain got reduced to a great extent and made me fit to go on my work. 

What makes more interesting is, he not only gave the treatment but gave me guidance on how to do preventative exercises such that the situation will never reoccur again. 

I recommend Drain Balraj Naidu of Onus Hospital to everyone. 

********** ************ ************
